<head>
		
	<texsetting wysiwyg="0"/><paper pagenumber="1" margin="20,20,20,25">A4</paper></head><body fontsize="12pt" fontface="ＭＳ Ｐ明朝">
<p>多変数の関数<mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>に対して、</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>=<mblock><munit entity="1">lim<mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit entity="1">rightarrow</munit><munit>0</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p>を<mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit></mblock>の<mblock><munit italic="1">x</munit></mblock>による偏微分と呼ぶ。</p>
<p/>
<p>今簡単のために、２変数の関数<mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>を考える。</p>
<p/>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p/>
<p>ここで平均値の定理を用いれば、</p>
<p/>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">f<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">x</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">theta<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">f<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">y</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">theta<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>(</munit><munit>0</munit><munit>&lt;</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">theta<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">theta<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>&lt;</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>と書けるから、式は</p>
<p/>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">f<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">x</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">theta<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">f<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">y</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">theta<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">Delta</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
